headline: Honeywell Aerospace on Europe, Japan & South Korea as defense markets
summary: Matthew Milas, president of Defense & Space at Honeywell Aerospace, says the company is investing heavily in higher capacity and innovation as countries around the world ramp up defense spending. He also drills down on the company's global footprint.
